Dialogue: 2,2:26:29.90,2:26:31.10,Default,,0,0,0,,放進去可以嗎？
Dialogue: 2,2:26:32.85,2:26:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,可以啊
Dialogue: 2,2:26:34.05,2:26:35.94,Default,,0,0,0,,可以的嗎？   -只不過有點尷尬... 
Dialogue: 2,2:26:53.50,2:26:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,糟了...
Dialogue: 2,2:26:59.13,2:27:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,還是讓我先舔一下吧
Dialogue: 2,2:27:37.94,2:27:39.18,Default,,0,0,0,,要進去了喲
Dialogue: 2,2:27:46.00,2:27:47.84,Default,,0,0,0,,放進哪裡？放進這裡嗎？
Dialogue: 2,2:27:51.68,2:27:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,啊˜進去了
Dialogue: 2,2:27:58.04,2:27:59.14,Default,,0,0,0,,你看
Dialogue: 2,2:28:10.59,2:28:12.26,Default,,0,0,0,,進到很深處了呢
Dialogue: 2,2:28:13.26,2:28:14.84,Default,,0,0,0,,啊˜好舒服
Dialogue: 2,2:28:21.63,2:28:23.07,Default,,0,0,0,,啊˜好舒服
